 2019-05102019-05-15,  ,  ,  ,  NRCAN
ActNational Energy Board Act
SubjectExtending the time limit - Dorsey International Power Line Project
PrecisOrder extending the legislated time limit for the Governor in Council decision on Manitoba Hydro's new DORSEY INTERNATIONAL POWER LINE proposed in Manitoba Hydro's application regarding the MANITOBA-MINNESOTA TRANSMISSION PROJECT by twenty-nine days, from May 16, 2019 to up to June 14, 2019.
